					<h1>ANGOLA DMC</h1>
					<p class="text-center">Last Places Angola is one of the first DMCs to operate in Angola since the country opened to tourism in 2012. Last Places Angola has been operating in Angola since 2014 offering tailor made trips to travel agencies from all around the World. Most of these trips are focused in Angola’s main highlights: tribal groups, nature and colonial heritage.</p>
